<paragraph blockId="3.[227,1436,958,1020]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">The species is named after the famous British traveler, journalist and explorer of Africa, Henry Morton Stanley, the Frst European who visited the Rwenzori Mountains in 1876.</paragraph>
